HEADWORD: Purfile
<hw>Pur"file</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Purfle</er>.]</ety> <def>A sort of ancient trimming of tinsel and
thread for women's gowns; -- called also
<altname>bobbinwork</altname>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Piers
Plowman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

